<h1>遐</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#cc7700;">xiá</span><span class=alesi>(xia2)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 遐 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 遐</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/afar" style="color:black;">afar</a>, <a href="/dictionary/distant" style="color:black;">distant</a>; <a href="/dictionary/old" style="color:black;">old</a>, advanced in</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 12<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 12 strokes: <a href="/character/就" title="jiu4: just, simply; to come, go to; to approach, near">就</a>, <a href="/character/道" title="dao4: path, road, street; method, way">道</a>, <a href="/character/然" title="ran2: yes, certainly; pledge, promise">然</a>, <a href="/character/最" title="zui4: most, extremely, exceedingly">最</a>, <a href="/character/等" title="">等</a>, <a href="/character/斯" title="si1: this, thus, such; to lop off; emphatic particle">斯</a>, <a href="/character/提" title="ti2: hold in hand; lift in hand">提</a>, <a href="/character/量" title="liang4: measure, quantity, capacity">量</a>, <a href="/character/期" title="qi1: period of time; date; time limit">期</a>, <a href="/character/强" title="qiang2: strong, powerful, energetic">强</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/辵" title="Kangxi radical 162">辵</a>&nbsp;162.9</p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 3852</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 5315</p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/升遐" title="sheng1 xia2">升遐</a>, <a href="/dictionary/登遐" title="deng1 xia2">登遐</a>, <a href="/dictionary/荒遐" title="huang1 xia2">荒遐</a>, <a href="/dictionary/遐布" title="xia2 bu4">遐布</a>, <a href="/dictionary/遐年" title="xia2 nian2">遐年</a>, <a href="/dictionary/遐心" title="xia2 xin1">遐心</a>, <a href="/dictionary/遐志" title="xia2 zhi4">遐志</a>, <a href="/dictionary/遐思" title="xia2 si1">遐思</a>, <a href="/dictionary/遐想" title="xia2 xiang3">遐想</a>, <a href="/dictionary/遐方" title="xia2 fang1">遐方</a>, <a href="/dictionary/遐弃" title="xia2 qi4">遐弃</a>, <a href="/dictionary/遐眺" title="xia2